  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our intrepid, ingenious crafter and explorer Flibbius  has always dreamt of taking to the sky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you use your wits, problem solving and creativity to help him find the Mysterious Flying Machine and finally make Flibbius' dreams come true?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/44e4e7a0aa546608a82124fe6aee9bcc.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short puzzle adventure game where you meet characters, craft items and  solve puzzles!  The game should take between 2 and 3 hours to complete, depending on your playstyle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/746a284c9406ac8a9ea72798dc64d1a5.poster.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/746a284c9406ac8a9ea72798dc64d1a5.webm?t=1755110829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/7bc7e2b2edeecdb7aff8ec4f0fe3e76a.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, delightful, adventure featuring our tortoisey protagonist Flibbius</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles! Find items, craft new ones & use them to solve puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a variety of wacky, wonderful and quirky characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A journal with secret puzzle hints in case you get a bit stuck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No time pressure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Works fantastically on steamdeck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/7f2757980b4cc668d92b2968482851e1.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span>Please join our discord channel if you want to keep up to date with our progress or ask us any questions! or follow our journey on any of our other social channels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/8a6dfbcb700b4189f80e2f52a45be69f.poster.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/8a6dfbcb700b4189f80e2f52a45be69f.webm?t=1755110829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/2af50d4f09681b74c9c5421a78f82596.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! This game was made by a husband and wife team and is completely independent and self-funded. We hope you enjoy playing it! Your support means so much to us and we'd love to hear what you think. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our intrepid, ingenious crafter and explorer Flibbius  has always dreamt of taking to the sky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you use your wits, problem solving and creativity to help him find the Mysterious Flying Machine and finally make Flibbius' dreams come true?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/44e4e7a0aa546608a82124fe6aee9bcc.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short puzzle adventure game where you meet characters, craft items and  solve puzzles!  The game should take between 2 and 3 hours to complete, depending on your playstyle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/746a284c9406ac8a9ea72798dc64d1a5.poster.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/746a284c9406ac8a9ea72798dc64d1a5.webm?t=1755110829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/7bc7e2b2edeecdb7aff8ec4f0fe3e76a.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, delightful, adventure featuring our tortoisey protagonist Flibbius</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles! Find items, craft new ones & use them to solve puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a variety of wacky, wonderful and quirky characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A journal with secret puzzle hints in case you get a bit stuck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No time pressure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Works fantastically on steamdeck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/7f2757980b4cc668d92b2968482851e1.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span>Please join our discord channel if you want to keep up to date with our progress or ask us any questions! or follow our journey on any of our other social channels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/8a6dfbcb700b4189f80e2f52a45be69f.poster.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/8a6dfbcb700b4189f80e2f52a45be69f.webm?t=1755110829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296920/extras/2af50d4f09681b74c9c5421a78f82596.avif?t=1755110829\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! This game was made by a husband and wife team and is completely independent and self-funded. We hope you enjoy playing it! Your support means so much to us and we'd love to hear what you think. </p>",
